title: Loverboy (1989) Patrick Dempsey (Opt.SpanSubs) Remastered
description:
<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0097790/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0097790/</a>


Optional Spanish subs in separate idx/sub files.

Classic crazy-comedy with a very young Patrick Dempsey (then 23), now known from Grey's Anatomy. A pizza delivery guy unwillingly starts an escort service for wealthy, stylish women. 

This was one of my favorite vhs comedies in the 1980s, but it has not been available on dvd in Europe, so I picked it up when visiting the U.S. recently.


Rip from new digitally remastered DVD, widescreen, good stereo.
Burn tested, runs well in my DivX player.
XviD 720x384, AC3.
